data.description: Now is the time to get this house. As tourist season gets here, inventory will be picked off and you may not get this opportunity again! Come make an offer on this delightful coastal retreat at 192 Antofagasta St. which offers low HOA fees and NO CDD fees! It is the epitome of comfort and serenity, offering an idyllic lifestyle in a highly sought-after location. All it takes is just vision, a little elbow grease and TLC! Priced well below comps because of needed repairs! But the upgrades already done include: A new roof (2021) and HVAC (2021), Granite counter tops in the kitchen, Hurricane Impact rated windows and doors, complete re-piping of house with Pex piping in 2013 and so much more!  Step inside to discover a thoughtfully designed interior with an abundance of space, showcasing a harmonious blend of modern convenience and coastal charm.  The main living area features an open concept layout, perfect for entertaining and creating lasting memories with family and friends.  The chef-inspired kitchen is adorned with stainless steel appliances and ample cabinetry making it a true culinary haven.  Unwind in the generously sized bedrooms, each offering a peaceful retreat after a long day.  The outdoor space is a true oasis, boasting a private backyard with lush landscaping and comforting pool, providing a serene ambiance for relaxation and outdoor gatherings.  Enjoy the proximity to the picturesque Peace River and Charlotte Harbor as well as various marinas; perfect for boating enthusiasts and those who love waterfront activities.  Nestled in the charming community of Deep Creek in Punta Gorda, this property offers easy access to a host of recreational activities, including: golfing, fishing, and water sports. Embrace the laid-back Florida lifestyle while still being within reach of major urban centers such as Fort Myers and Sarasota.   Don't Miss Out on this rare opportunity to own a beautiful home in Punta Gorda that won't last long. Whether you're seeking a permanent residence or a vacation getaway, 192 Antofagasta St is the ideal choice for those who appreciate comfort, beauty, and the allure of coastal living. Charlotte Regional airport is just minutes away and Fort Myers International Airport is less than 30 minutes with easy access.  Inside add a touch of owners artistic design and paint colors to make this home your very own retreat. The price has been adjusted to account for the remaining repairs that are needed.
